OL,5, Regulated train fares in England will  
OL,6, rise below the rate of inflation next  
OL,7, year to help people with the cost of   
OL,8, living crisis, the government has said.
OL,10,FBefore the Covid pandemic, fares were  
OL,11,Fraised in January each year, based on  
OL,12,Fthe retail prices index (RPI) measure  
OL,13,Fof inflation from the previous July.   
OL,15,FThe normal formula is RPI plus 1%. RPI 
OL,16,Fin June was 11.8% - but it is not known
OL,17,Fwhat next year's increase will be.     
OL,19,FAs well as being lower than RPI, the   
OL,20,Fincrease will be delayed until March.  
